						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in the street in the village.</p>						

						<p>Kṛishṇarāya, 1527 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 14[48], Vyaya Āshāḍha, śu. 5, Sunday,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1526 A.D., June 15, Friday (not Sunday).</hi></p>						

						<p>Much damaged. It seems to record a gift as a <hi rend="italic">śrōtriya</hi> to a Brāhmaṇa.</p>						

						</summary>
